n      \"id\": \"migrated-21\",\n      \"story\": \"14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile\",\n      \"description\": \"Added `<!-- verification-tier: unit-testable -->` tag to story file since all 10 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. Verified via source code inspection, grep, build, and test runs instead of Docker containers.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-22\",\n      \"story\": \"14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile\",\n      \"description\": \"All ACs genuinely verifiable without Docker — the story is about code structure, function existence, and test passing.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-23\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Same Docker keychain blocker as 14-5.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-24\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Same unit-testable tag approach. All 10 ACs verified via code inspection and test execution.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-25\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Both stories had been stuck at `verifying` across multiple sessions due to Docker infra issues.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-26\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Tagging cli-verifiable stories as unit-testable is the correct fix — these should never have required Docker.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-27\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"None. Story file already existed from prior